QuestData.Title: Zanchuli Traitors
QuestData.Description: Dey are trying to cast down our loa, claiming dem to be false gods.$b$bDey have turned to de old ways of blood, sacrifice, and subjugation.$b$bI cannot even begin to say how offensive dis is. Kill any of dese traitors you find.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Wardruid Loti in Zanchul.
